channel.title: Another crafting interface is missing
channel.description:
Does anyone know where the interface is for the tanning? I can't ever see a good picture of it, but I think it looks like the one used for leather-crafting. If it is, all I have to do is change the words and the pictures. Otherwise I need the interface ID for it. Surely someone has found it...
Also, my question about interface 4161 is still unanswered. To bring it back up, is there a way to make interface 4161 display the jewelry instead of the required moulds. And don't say "Just replace the text and pictures" because that won't work. There must be a specific subframe or something.
